title: Clubs
body: Part of 2 clubs but neither show up on my profile as me being signed in or if one of my friends also has a look over. I cant switch clubs between the 2 I am part of.{{summoner:14}}

replies.body:
Hey there,

You'll have to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support about this issue as we here on the boards are unable to assist with account specific inquiries.
